          <text><![CDATA[<p><b>Battery Storage Innovation Act</b></p> <p>This bill amends the Energy Policy Act of 2005 to expand the categories of projects that are eligible for innovative technology loan guarantees to include a category of projects for battery storage technologies for residential, industrial, or transportation applications.</p>]]></text>
